ElementDescription: The NDAR Global Unique Identifier (GUID) for research subject
Subject ID how it's defined in lab/project
Date on which the interview/genetic test/sampling/imaging/biospecimen was completed. MM/DD/YYYY
Age in months at the time of the interview/test/sampling/imaging.
Notes: Age is rounded to chronological month. If the research participant is 15-days-old at time of interview, the appropriate value would be 0 months. If the participant is 16-days-old, the value would be 1 month.

ElementDescription: Sex of subject at birth
Notes: M = Male; F = Female; O=Other; NR = Not reported

ElementDescription: Think of the occasion you drank the most this PAST MONTH. How MUCH did you drink?
Notes: 0=0 drinks; 1=1 drink; 2=2 drinks; 25=25 or more drinks; 777=refuse to answer

ElementDescription: Think of the occasion you drank the most during the PAST MONTH. How many HOURS did you spend drinking on that occasion?
Notes: 0=Less than 1 hour; 1=1 hour; 2=2 hours; 10=10+ hours; 777=refuse to answer

ElementDescription: How many days did you drink alcohol during the past month?
On a given occasion during the past month, how much alcohol did you typically drink?
Notes: 0= 0 drinks; 1= 1 drink; 2= 2 drinks; 25= 25 or more drinks; -5= Item seen but not answered; -999= Data not submitted (incomplete, item not seen)

ElementDescription: On a given occasion during the past month, how many hours did you spend drinking?
Notes: 0= Less than 1 hour; 1= 1 hour; 2= 2 hours; 10= 10+ hours; -5= Item seen but not answered; -999= Data not submitted (incomplete, item not seen)

ElementDescription: On a given weekend evening during the past month, how much alcohol did you typically drink?
Notes: 0=0 drinks; 1=1 drink; 2=2 drinks; 25=25 or more drinks

ElementDescription: On a given weekend evening during the past month, how many hours did you spend drinking?
Notes: 0=Less than 1 hour; 1=1 hour; 2=2 hours; 10=10+ hours

ElementDescription: Think of the occasion you drank the most the past 2 months. How MUCH did you drink?
Notes: 0=0 drinks; 1= 1 drink; 25=25 or more drinks; -5=item seen but not answered; -999=data not submitted (incomplete, item not seen)

ElementDescription: Think of the occasion you drank the most the past 2 months. How many HOURS did you spend drinking on that occasion?
Notes: 0=0 hours; 1=1 hour; 10=10 or more hours; -5=item seen but not answered; -999=data not submitted (incomplete, item not seen)

ElementDescription: How many days of the week did you drink alcohol during the past 2 months?
Notes: 0=I did not drink at all; 1=Once a month; 2=Twice a month; 3=Three times a month; 4=Once a week; 5=Twice a week; 6=Three times a week; 7=Four times a week; 8=Five times a week; 9=Six times a week; 10=Every day; -5=item seen but not answered; -999=data not submitted (incomplete, item not seen)

ElementDescription: During the past 2 months, how often have you had 4 (if female or intersex)/5 (if male) or more drinks in about 2 hours?
Notes: 0=Never; 1=Once a month; 2=Twice a month; 3=Three times a month; 4=Once a week; 5=Twice a week; 6=Three times a week; 7=Four times a week; 8=Five times a week; 9=Six times a week; 10=Every day; -5=item seen but not answered; -999=data not submitted (incomplete, item not seen)

ElementDescription: During the past 2 months, how often have you had 8 (if female or intersex)/10 (if male) or more drinks in about 2 hours?
Notes: 0=Never; 1=Once a month; 2=Twice a month; 3=Three times a month; 4=Once a week; 5=Twice a week; 6=Three times a week; 7=Four times a week; 8=Five times a week; 9=Six times a week; 10=Every day; -5=item seen but not answered; -999=data not submitted (incomplete, item not seen)

ElementDescription: During the past month, how often have you had 4 (if you were assigned female at birth) or 5 (if you were assigned male at birth) or more drinks in about 2 hours?
Notes: 0=Never; 1=Once a month; 2=Two times a month; 3=Three times a month; 4=Once a week; 5=Twice a week; 6=Three times a week; 7=Four times a week; 8=Five times a week; 9=Six times a week; 10=Every day; -5=Item seen but not answered; -999=Data not submitted (incomplete, item not seen)

ElementDescription: During the past month, how often have you had 8 (if you were assigned female at birth) or 10 (if you were assigned male at birth) or more drinks in about 2 hours?
Notes: 0=Never; 1=Once a month; 2=Two times a month; 3=Three times a month; 4=Once a week; 5=Twice a week; 6=Three times a week; 7=Four times a week; 8=Five times a week; 9=Six times a week; 10=Every day; -5=Item seen but not answered; -999=Data not submitted (incomplete, item not seen)

ElementDescription: Timepoint/visit label
Notes: e.g., Baseline, Morning, At Bedtime

ElementDescription: How many days of the week did you drink alcohol during the past month?
Notes: 0=I did not drink at all; 1=Once a month; 2=Two times a month; 3=Three times a month; 4=Once a week; 5=Twice a week; 6=Three times a week; 7=Four times a week; 8=Five times a week; 9=Six times a week; 10=Every day; -5=Item seen but not answered; -999=Data not submitted (incomplete, item not seen)

ElementDescription: Think of the occasion (within a 24 hour period) you drank the most in the past 3 months. How many drinks did you have?
Notes: Number of drinks; 20=20 or more drinks

ElementDescription: Think of the occasion (within a 24 hour period) you drank the most in the past 3 months. How many hours did you spend drinking on the occasion?
Notes: Number of hours; 10=10 or more hours

ElementDescription: At what age did you first drink enough alcohol to feel drunk?
Notes: Age in years; 0=I have never felt drunk; 9=Before 10 years old; -9=Prefer not to answer

ElementDescription: How frequently did you drink alcohol during the PAST MONTH?
Notes: 0= I did not drink at all; 0.25= Once a month; 0.5= Two times a month; 0.75= Three times a month; 1= Once a week; 2= Twice a week; 3= Three times a week; 4= Four times a week; 5= Five times a week; 6= Six times a week; 7= Every day; -5= Item seen but not answered; -999= Data not submitted (incomplete, item not seen)
